        Constructor of metric snapshot
        Parameters:
        _measureReducer - measure reducer used to create this metric snaphot
        _name - metric name
        _accumulatedSamples - accumulation of all samples used to create this metric
        _samplingSize - sampling size used to generate this metric snapshot
        _totalHits - total number of measures since metric creation
        _maxMeasure - maximum measure get of all samples used
        _minMeasure - minimum measure get of all samples used
        _averageMeasure - average measure value over all samples used
        _lastMeasure - last taken measure
        _lastOccurrence - timestamp of the last taken measure
